{
  "video_id": "wjW-v0IPT_M",
  "title": "David Hanson: Robots that \"show emotion\"",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 16260.000000000002,
      "end_time": 19260.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m Dr. David Hanson, and I build robots with character."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "And by that, I mean"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "that I develop robots that are characters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "but also robots that will eventually"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "come to empathize with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re starting with a variety of technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "that have converged into these conversational character robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "that can see faces, make eye contact with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "make a full range of facial expressions, understand speech"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "and begin to model how you&#39;re feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 46260.0,
      "text": "and who you are, and build a relationship with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46260.0,
      "end_time": 48260.0,
      "text": "I developed a series of technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48260.0,
      "end_time": 51260.0,
      "text": "that allowed the robots to make more realistic facial expressions"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "than previously achieved, on lower power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "which enabled the walking biped robots, the first androids."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "So, it&#39;s a full range of facial expressions"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "simulating all the major muscles in the human face,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "running on very small batteries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "extremely lightweight."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "The materials that allowed the battery-operated facial expressions"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68260.0,
      "end_time": 70260.0,
      "text": "is a material that we call Frubber,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "and it actually has three major innovations"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "in the material that allow this to happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "One is hierarchical pores,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 80260.0,
      "text": "and the other is a macro-molecular nanoscale porosity in the material."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "There he&#39;s starting to walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 86260.0,
      "text": "This is at the Korean Advanced Institute of Science and Technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 86260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "I built the head. They built the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 93260.0,
      "text": "So the goal here is to achieve sentience in machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 93260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "and not just sentience, but empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re working with the Machine Perception Laboratory"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "at the U.C. San Diego."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 104260.0,
      "text": "They have this really remarkable facial expression technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104260.0,
      "end_time": 106260.0,
      "text": "that recognizes facial expressions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "what facial expressions you&#39;re making."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "It also recognizes where you&#39;re looking, your head orientation."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111260.0,
      "end_time": 113260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re emulating all the major facial expressions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "and then controlling it with the software"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "that we call the Character Engine."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 121260.0,
      "text": "And here is a little bit of the technology that&#39;s involved in that."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121260.0,
      "end_time": 129259.0,
      "text": "In fact, right now -- plug it from here, and then plug it in here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 129258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "and now let&#39;s see if it gets my facial expressions."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132260.0,
      "end_time": 137260.0,
      "text": "Okay. So I&#39;m smiling."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 137260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "Now I&#39;m frowning."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "And this is really heavily backlit."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "Okay, here we go."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "Oh, it&#39;s so sad."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "Okay, so you smile, frowning."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 154260.0,
      "text": "So his perception of your emotional states"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 154260.0,
      "end_time": 158260.0,
      "text": "is very important for machines to effectively become empathetic."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 158260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "Machines are becoming devastatingly capable"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "of things like killing. Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 167260.0,
      "text": "Those machines have no place for empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 167260.0,
      "end_time": 169260.0,
      "text": "And there is billions of dollars being spent on that."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 169260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "Character robotics could plant the seed"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "for robots that actually have empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 175260.0,
      "text": "So, if they achieve human level intelligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "or, quite possibly, greater than human levels of intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 182260.0,
      "text": "this could be the seeds of hope for our future."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182260.0,
      "end_time": 186260.0,
      "text": "So, we&#39;ve made 20 robots in the last eight years, during the course of getting my Ph.D."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "And then I started Hanson Robotics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "which has been developing these things for mass manufacturing."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "This is one of our robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "that we showed at Wired NextFest a couple of years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 199260.0,
      "text": "And it sees multiple people in a scene,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 199260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "remembers where individual people are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "and looks from person to person, remembering people."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "So, we&#39;re involving two things."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "One, the perception of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "and two, the natural interface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 215260.0,
      "text": "the natural form of the interface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 215260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "so that it&#39;s more intuitive for you to interact with the robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 221260.0,
      "text": "You start to believe that it&#39;s alive and aware."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 221260.0,
      "end_time": 224260.0,
      "text": "So one of my favorite projects was bringing all this stuff together"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 224260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "in an artistic display of an android portrait"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "of science-fiction writer Philip K. Dick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "who wrote great works like, \"Do Androids Dream of Electric Sheep?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 234260.0,
      "text": "which was the basis of the movie \"Bladerunner.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 234260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "In these stories, robots often think"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "that they&#39;re human, and they sort of come to life."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 242260.0,
      "text": "So we put his writings, letters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 242260.0,
      "end_time": 245260.0,
      "text": "his interviews, correspondences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 245260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "into a huge database of thousands of pages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 249260.0,
      "text": "and then used some natural language processing"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 249260.0,
      "end_time": 251260.0,
      "text": "to allow you to actually have a conversation with him."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 251260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "And it was kind of spooky, because he would say these things"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "that just sounded like they really understood you."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 259260.0,
      "text": "And this is one of the most exciting projects that we&#39;re developing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 259260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "which is a little character that&#39;s a spokesbot"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "for friendly artificial intelligence, friendly machine intelligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re getting this mass-manufactured."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 270260.0,
      "text": "We specked it out to actually be doable"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 270260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "with a very, very low-cost bill of materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 277260.0,
      "text": "so that it can become a childhood companion for kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 277260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "Interfacing with the Internet, it gets smarter over the years."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "As artificial intelligence evolves, so does his intelligence."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 285260.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: Thank you so much. That&#39;s incredible."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 285260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}